  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Orthopedic Tibial Tray CFD Credibility Assessment (MRL 3, NC-4 Clean Package)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for finite-element and CFD-assisted prediction of tibial tray stress distribution in a total knee arthroplasty (TKA) implant under physiological loading. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can predict peak von Mises stress and contact pressure at the tibial plateau interface for a Class II orthopedic device at Model Risk Level 3. All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors are assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels for MRL 3. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed on material property inputs. Decision: Accepted.",
